OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FBlustery
OL,6,Fshowers continuing this evening
OL,7,Fgradually fading during the first half
OL,8,Fof the night. Drier with clear spells
OL,9,Fto follow. The wind eases but
OL,10,Fremaining breezy over high ground and
OL,11,Falong the coast.
OL,12,
OL,13,CFriday:FA dry and bright start to the
OL,14,Fday. Showers developing by the
OL,15,Fafternoon interspersed with some sunny
OL,16,Fspells. Clouding over by the evening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
